author: Cleo Abram
description:
3I/Atlas, the interstellar comet, has sparked a lot of theories and let our imaginations run a bit wild. Recent reports have been focusing on the odd behavior of the comet’s tail. Some say it’s disappeared and others say it’s pointing in the wrong direction. So what’s going on? 

Subscribe to learn more!

#3iAtlas #comet #interstellar #aliens #space #shorts
title: What’s Up With 3I/Atlas’s Tail?
